# JR Referee Clinics

Full program map: `docs/jr-ref/README.md`

## Systems

| Layer | Source |
|-------|--------|
| Registration | Fillout.com → **127SI - JR REF** Airtable |
| Source of truth | Airtable base `JR_REF_AIRTABLE_BASE_ID` |
| Public web | hoopchallenges.com `/jr-referee-clinics` (same Vercel project as hub) |
| GitHub | This repo — `airtable/schema/jr-ref/`, `docs/jr-ref/`, `web/lib/jr-ref/` |

## Before editing Airtable field names in web code

1. Run `tools/airtable/jr-ref/export_schema.py -v`
2. Read `airtable/schema/jr-ref/snapshots/<latest>/schema_doc_*.md`
3. Update `airtable/schema/jr-ref/current/field-map.md`

## Web rules

- Use `lib/jr-ref/airtable.ts` — **not** `lib/airtable/client.ts` (Shooting Challenge base)
- Read `web/docs/jr-ref/public-data-rules.md` before exposing fields
- Nav: `lib/navigation/jr-referee-clinics-nav.ts`

## Automations

Same script standard as Shooting Challenge: `airtable/automations/AUTOMATION_SCRIPT_STANDARD.md`

New scripts go in `airtable/automations/jr-referee-clinics/`.

## Statewide expansion

See `docs/jr-ref/state-wide-expansion.md` for geography, seasons, and publish-flag requirements.
